 \tan \phi \ = \ \tan( \alpha - \beta ) \ = \ \frac{\tan \alpha \ - \ \tan \beta}{1 \ + \ \tan \alpha \cdot \tan \beta} \ = \ \frac{\sqrt{3} \ - \ \frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}}{1 \ + \ \sqrt{3} \cdot \frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}} \ = \ \frac{ \frac{3 \ - \ 2}{\sqrt{3}}}{1 \ + \ 2 } \ = \ \frac{1}{3 \ \sqrt{3}} \ .  
